items.synopsis: Former US president Donald Trump is indicted on criminal charges. Follow live.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Donald Trump has been indicted on four counts tied to efforts to undermine 2020 election, including "conspiracy to defraud" the US. The former US president has been summoned to appear in federal court on August 3 (local time), the Justice Department says.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: Donald Trump indicted by grand jury over attempts to overturn 2020 election

tied to efforts to undermine 2020 election, including "conspiracy to defraud" the US.
The former US president has been summoned to appear in federal court on August 3 (local time), the Justice Department says.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Good morning. A grand jury investigating attempts to stop the lawful transfer of power following the 2020 US presidential election has indicted at least one person. Former US president Donald Trump had earlier said he was expecting to be indicted today. However, the indictment is sealed and it is not known who it refers to. We'll have more details throughout this morning.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: Grand jury hands up indictment against unnamed defendant in January 6 probe

children.content: Good morning. A grand jury investigating attempts to stop the lawful transfer of power following the 2020 US presidential election has indicted
Former US president Donald Trump had earlier said he was expecting to be indicted today.
However, the indictment is sealed and it is not known who it refers to.
We'll have more details throughout this morning.
